axiom df-exid(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2) {
  ⊢ ExId = { s0 | ∃(s1 ∈ dom(dom(s0)), ∀(s2 ∈ dom(dom(s0)),((s1[s0]s2)= s2 ∧(s2[s0]s1)= s2)))}
